            <object type="motiv" xml:id="m.2017.1">
               <objectIdentifier>
                  <idno type="invNo"/>
               </objectIdentifier>
               <objectContents>
                  <ab type="description">We see the living quarters of several workers (all men on the pictures). There are beds (for 5 people), including one bunk bed, as well as two cooking stove and dinner table. Each picture shows 2-3 workers and 1-3 visitors. The workers show their living conditions, and the visitor also try the workers’ food. The group is often having conversation. The room looks spacious, but also in bad condition. The workers also dry their clothes on a wire between a sleeping bed and another item (that is out of the frame). A map of Yugoslavia can be seen on the wall, as well as a mirror. It is unclear whether the accommodation space is rented or if it is the company’s property.</ab>
               </objectContents>
